Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:




Three 10 tall robots stood next to each other, talking.


Imprisoner, the leader, was completely green, brown, and tan.
"We have to capture someone, and get information out of them."

Predator growled, showing his fangs, a trait of all jaguars.
"No!", he yelled, his tawny and spotted body raising both of his arms, "I 
think we should just go to the Maximals.  After all, most of the bounties ARE 
on Predeacons."

Choran, his body scaly, yellow and orange and green, his teeth long, very 
sharp looking (not to mention deadly looking), and many.
"I agree with Predator, Imprisoner.  We should go to the Maximals and get the 
locations, then turn around and shoot them if necessary." his voice sounding 
like he was talking in water.

"Fine!  If you're going to twist my hand so hard.  Scans showed four crashed 
ships.  One with a Maximal transwarp signature, the other Autobot.  That's 
obviously the Ark.  And there are two Predacon, one is Hell Beast's ship.  
The other, I have no idea."

"Let's head to the Ark." Choran said in his gurgly voice.

"Alright." Imrpisoner said followed by a nod, the bounty hunters heading for 
the Ark.
